title: Memphis Bleek and Casanova Interview and more
itunes:title: Memphis Bleek and Casanova Interview and more
description:
Monday 10/30- Today on the show we had Memphis Bleek and Casanova stop by where they spoke about their new project with on Ware House Music Group, trust issues and more. Also, since Charlamagne was not here we gave our listeners a chance to call up and shout whoever they want to give "Donkey of the Day" to. Moreover, it is Monday so you know we had "Shoot Your Shot" and this time a fitness trainer was trying to shoot his shot at his client.
